data.title: Dental Care Jacksonville Beach
data.meta_description: Parker & Pennington provides the best dental care available. We offer General, Cosmetic & Implant Dentistry in Ponte Vedra, Atlantic Beach & Jacksonville.
data.text:
When it comes to taking care of our patients, we intentionally go the extra mile. We set the highest standards for ourselves and for our patients’ health and believe in doing our “best and finest” dental care for your long term health for every patient, every time, all the time without fail or exception. That’s simply what our patients deserve and it’s what we’d want for ourselves too.

When you invest in your health and well-being, you’ll always feel confident in your decision knowing we always have your best interest at heart and in mind!

When you choose Parker & Pennington Dentistry, you can expect:

A comfortable, yet professional atmosphere

Compassionate dentists and team

Highly personalized loving care

Expert diagnostics and advice

Modern advanced dentistry in a family friendly comfortable environment

Fully customized and individualized long health plans

An experience where you feel and are listened to and understood

Our patients appreciate the time and high levels of care we put into their treatments. Our dentists and team are highly skilled and professional and we even go one step beyond that. We are compassionate, dedicated, and will strive to exceed expectations. We truly care about the needs, comforts, and concerns of our patients and most of all will be your guide to making smart proactive decisions about your overall long term complete and optimal health.

Our patients continue to come back to us year after year because we treat them like family with the utmost care, love and respect. They often tell us that they have never before experienced the level of service and care we will provide you. We always say with us you’ll always get the truth, have our commitment and a promise of fun, yes, even at the dentist.

After all, when you’ve got one life and one mouth and you are an extraordinary human being you deserve nothing less than the very best and most extraordinary oral health and dental care possible and that’s what you’ll get here with us.

That’s The Parker and Pennington Way.

And we’re excited to meet you and for you to experience it first hand, yourself.
